About
=====

Lightweight, easy-to-deploy and hackable TCP chatting server. It is designed for small to medium communities.

Protocol
========

`ax` uses its own protocol. Message formatting is same for both server and client:

class Payload:
    message: str
    args: list[str]

Example `payload.message`: NEW_USER_MESSAGE
Example `payload.args`: [<author>, <content>]
Unparsed: NEW_USER_MESSAGE|dylan|hello